"&ktalkd; стандартно поставляется в составе "
"проекта &kde; <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.kde.org\">http://www.kde.org</ulink> и входит в "
"пакет kdenetwork."

#: index.docbook:516
msgid ""
"You can always download the latest &ktalkd; from the main &FTP; site of the "
"&kde; project, <ulink "
"url=\"ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde\">ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde</ulink>"
" and from its mirrors. It's usually found in <ulink "
"url=\"ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/stable/latest/apps/network\">"
"ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/stable/latest/apps/network</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Вы всегда можете скачать последнюю "
"версию &ktalkd; с главного &FTP; сайта проекта "
"&kde;, <ulink "
"url=\"ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde\">ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde</ulink> или "
"одного из его зеркал. Он обычно находится "
"в <ulink "
"url=\"ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/stable/latest/apps/network\">"
"ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/stable/latest/apps/network</ulink>"

#: index.docbook:526
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Требования"

#: index.docbook:528
msgid ""
"In order to successfully compile &ktalkd;, you need the latest versions of "
"the &kde; libraries as well as the &Qt; C++ library. All required libraries "
"as well as ktalkd itself can be found on <ulink "
"url=\"ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/\">ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Для успешной компиляции &ktalkd; вам "
"необходима последняя версия &kde; и "
"библиотеки &Qt;. Все библиотеки и сам ktalkd "
"можно найти на <ulink "
"url=\"ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/\">ftp://ftp.kde.org/pub/kde/</ulink>."

#: index.docbook:537
msgid "Compilation and Installation"
msgstr "Сборка и установка"

#: index.docbook:539
msgid ""
"In order to compile and install &ktalkd; on your system, type the following "
"in the base directory of the &ktalkd; distribution:"
msgstr ""
"Чтобы собрать и установить &ktalkd; в вашей "
"системе, наберите следующее в корневом "
"каталоге дистрибутива &ktalkd;:"

#: index.docbook:544
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>./configure</command></userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>make</command></userinput> \n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>make</command> "
"<option>install</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>./configure</command></userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>make</command></userinput> \n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>make</command> "
"<option>install</option></userinput>"

#: index.docbook:550
msgid ""
"As &ktalkd; is a daemon, <userinput><command>make</command> "
"<option>install</option></userinput> will require <systemitem "
"class=\"username\">root</systemitem> privileges."
msgstr ""
"Поскольку &ktalkd; - демон, то для "
"<userinput><command>make</command> <option>install</option></userinput> "
"потребуются права <systemitem "
"class=\"username\">root</systemitem>."

#: index.docbook:556
msgid ""
"Don't forget to update <filename>/etc/inetd.conf</filename>"
". For example, on a &Linux; system, if &kde; is in <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/opt/kde</filename>, change the lines concerning "
"<command>talk</command> and <command>ntalk</command> to:"
msgstr ""
"Не забудьте обновить файл "
"<filename>/etc/inetd.conf</filename>. На пример, в &Linux;, "
"если &kde; находится в <filename "
"class=\"directory\">/opt/kde</filename>, измените строки, "
"касающиеся <command>talk</command> и <command>ntalk</command> "
"на:"

#: index.docbook:563
msgid ""
"talk   dgram   udp     wait    root    /usr/sbin/tcpd  /opt/kde/bin/kotalkd\n"
"ntalk  dgram   udp     wait    root    /usr/sbin/tcpd  /opt/kde/bin/ktalkd"
msgstr ""
"talk   dgram   udp     wait    root    /usr/sbin/tcpd  /opt/kde/bin/kotalkd\n"
"ntalk  dgram   udp     wait    root    /usr/sbin/tcpd  /opt/kde/bin/ktalkd"

#: index.docbook:568
msgid ""
"A script is provided, to make the necessary change automatically. Update "
"your <filename>inetd.conf</filename> file just by running"
msgstr ""
"Скрипт должен произвести все необходимые "
"изменения автоматически. Обновите "
"<filename>inetd.conf</filename> запустив"

#: index.docbook:573
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> "
"<userinput><command>./post-install.sh</command></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> "
"<userinput><command>./post-install.sh</command></userinput>"

#: index.docbook:577
msgid ""
"Anyway, you'll have to <emphasis>restart inetd</emphasis> after this. On "
"most &Linux; systems, do:"
msgstr ""
"В любом случае вам потребуется после "
"этого <emphasis>перезапустить inetd</emphasis>. В "
"большинстве систем &Linux; необходимо "
"набрать:"

#: index.docbook:581
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>killall</command> <option>-HUP "
"inetd</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>killall</command> <option>-HUP "
"inetd</option></userinput>"

#: index.docbook:585
msgid ""
"On newer systems, using <command>xinetd</command>, there is no more "
"<filename>/etc/inetd.conf</filename>, and you should edit or create "
"<filename>/etc/xinetd.d/talk</filename> instead, with those lines:"
msgstr ""
"В новых системах, которые используют "
"<command>xinetd</command>, больше не существует "
"<filename>/etc/inetd.conf</filename>, и вы должны "
"отредактировать или создать файл "
"<filename>/etc/xinetd.d/talk</filename>, заменив следующие "
"строки:"

#: index.docbook:591
msgid ""
"service talk\n"
"{\n"
"\tsocket_type = dgram\n"
"\twait = yes\n"
"\tuser = root\n"
"\tserver = /usr/bin/kotalkd\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"service ntalk\n"
"{\n"
"\tsocket_type = dgram\n"
"\twait = yes\n"
"\tuser = root\n"
"\tserver = /usr/bin/ktalkd\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"service talk\n"
"{\n"
"\tsocket_type = dgram\n"
"\twait = yes\n"
"\tuser = root\n"
"\tserver = /usr/bin/kotalkd\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"service ntalk\n"
"{\n"
"\tsocket_type = dgram\n"
"\twait = yes\n"
"\tuser = root\n"
"\tserver = /usr/bin/ktalkd\n"
"}"

#: index.docbook:609
msgid "then restart <command>xinetd</command>."
msgstr "а затем перезапустить <command>xinetd</command>."

